title: Bobby Finally Pranks Caitlin + Amy Accidentally Calls 911 ON THE AIR! + 90’s Country Guitar Solo Game + Bobby Got The Vaccine
itunes:title: Bobby Finally Pranks Caitlin + Amy Accidentally Calls 911 ON THE AIR! + 90’s Country Guitar Solo Game + Bobby Got The Vaccine
description:
Bobby finally pranked Caitlin last night and shared the audio with us today. He got her good! Bobby talks about getting the vaccine yesterday and how everyone was so nice! Amy was showing us a life hack on her phone and accidentally called 911 on the air. We all freak out at what she did next…We play a couple rounds of the 90’s Country guitar solo game! Bobby plays a famous guitar solo from a 90’s country song and the show has to name the song!
